<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-TX8t27EcRE3e/ihU7zmQxVncDAy5uIKz4rEkgIXeMed4M0jlfIDPvg6uqKI2xXr2" crossorigin="anonymous">
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container text-center">
      <div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518933165971-611dbc9c412d?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1189&q=80); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-position: center center;">
        <div class="container">
          <h1 style="color:white;"><strong>Mickael Joseph</strong></h1><br>
          <h3 style="color:white;">développeur web full-stack junior</h3>
          <%=image_tag "moi.png", class: "photo"%>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarTogglerDemo03" aria-controls="navbarTogglerDemo03" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Home</a>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarTogglerDemo03">
          <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto mt-2 mt-lg-0">
            <li class="nav-item active">
              <a class="nav-link" href="#">Formation <span class="sr-only">(current)</span></a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="#">Site</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <form class="form-inline my-2 my-lg-0">
            <input class="form-control mr-sm-2" type="search" placeholder="Search" aria-label="Search">
            <button class="btn btn-outline-light my-2 my-sm-0" type="submit">Search</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2>Mes formations</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between mt-5 text-center">
      <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
        <%=image_tag "udemy.png", class: "card-img-top"%>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">ruby on rails <br>wordpress</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
        <%=image_tag "wagon.jpg", class: "card-img-top"%>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">Ruby on rails <br>SQL <br>HTML <br>CSS <br>Javascript <br>Boostrap</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
        <%=image_tag "codeacademy.png", class: "card-img-top"%>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">Html <br> CSS <br> Javascript <br>Ruby <br> PHP</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div><br>
    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between mt-5">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Mon parcours</h2><br>
        <p>Anciennement préparateur en pharmacie, j'ai entamé une reconversion pour devenir développeur web.
         J'ai commencé par une formation avec le wagon a Lille pour devenir développeur web fullstack sur
         ruby on rails , <br>
         j'y ai notament appris SQL, html, css, javascript, boostrap, et connaissance de base en ux.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
      <h2>Ce que j'aime dans le <\dev></h2><br>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <%=image_tag "teamwork.jpg", class: "dev"%>
              <h5>teamwork</h5>
              <p>Collaborer et échanger pour réaliser un projet.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
              <%=image_tag "teck.jpg", class: "dev"%>
              <h5>nouvelle technologie</h5>
              <p>Apprendre les nouveaux languages et leur evolution.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-100"></div>
            <div class="col">
            <%=image_tag "varieté.jpg", class: "dev"%>
            <h5>varieté</h5>
            <p>Chaque projet est different dans son approche et son execution.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
            <%=image_tag "com.jpg", class: "dev"%>
              <h5>communauté</h5>
              <p>La communauté du développement web est très collaborative.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container text-center">
      <%= link_to "" do %><%= image_tag 'GitHub.png', class: "logo m-5" %><%end %>
      <%= link_to "" do %><%= image_tag 'linkedin.png',class: "logo m-5" %><%end %>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>